                                            <li>• 🔑 Bcrypt password hashing</li>
                                            <li>• 🛡️ Role-based access control</li>
                                            <li>• 📱 Secure session management</li>
                                            <li>• 🔒 Regular security audits</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">View our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for complete details.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
